# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

JSA_CATALOGUE - Create a JSA style catalogue

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe takes a set of maps and produces JSA style 'extent' and
'peak' catalogues for each of them. It uses stilts to manipulate
catalogues produced by CUPID FINDCLUMPS.


NOT YET IMPLEMENTED: cross
references between maps.


